text: come here for the worst caipng and food selection. don't believe the other reviewers. those are before this new company took over. they only sell caipng, china food and one meepok/fishball noodle stall. meepok stall taste normal nth fantastic but wa the caipng can rly make u feel damn sick to the stomach because wtf standard is that..when i have 20min lunch time i got no choice but to eat here bcs its just downstairs my office. always regret after but i literally have no choice but to stomach the food bcs im starving. please change company pls. this food sux im honestly affected lol. i've never tasted such bad food in my life.
i love this coffeeshop (on the 3rd floor). lots of varieties, fish soup is famous, bak chor mee is authentic, pork chop rice is good. cai fan is cheap.
